title: Fish and Chips, Two Adventurous Cats Who Love Exploring the Great Outdoors With Their Humans
text:
A post shared by Fish & Chips (@adventuresoffishandchips) on Mar 14, 2017 at 9:25am PDT 

Fish and Chips are a couple of adventurous kitties who enjoy exploring the great outdoors on and around their home Vancouver Island and elsewhere with their devoted humans. Both cats are as equally comfortable walking on a leash as they are riding on their humansâ€™ backpacks and even on their shoulders and in their arms .
